{"tid":2033812,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"開始多五毛開BNO Post分化 97後 97前","createTime":"2020-05-25T01:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T14:31:22.000Z","uid":65139,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5c5c612b540ac431aadd83e5b9b414393f103df1","tid":2033812,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:23:42.000Z","msg":"「97前背信棄義<br />\n97後慘被遺棄」？<br />\n<br />\n五毛係咪岸鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實有冇BNO實際上都唔驚<br />\n<br />\n因為「香港人」唔係用政權/地理劃分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人係一樣概念、一個精神、一種價值<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Ideas are bulletproof.<br />\n<br />\nWhen it is circle, be it circle.<br />\nWhen it is square, be it square.<br />\nBe it Water as always.<br />\nBe water my friends.</span>"},{"pid":"171b0a892d8846b2b36e88e5a5d02df5647cfdf4","tid":2033812,"uid":226304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:40:44.000Z","msg":"好多熱狗式分化L 出沒"},{"pid":"2e607de742a40999bae4c2a1027bb09d5b700816","tid":2033812,"uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:04:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BNO平權正視聽</span></span><br />\n連登一向有大量風向L、放負L，睇到BNO平權消息就用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>割97後等風向挑撥離間</strong></span>，大家上連登請帶埋個腦。<br />\n<br />\n我從六月開始打英國戰線，希望嚮呢度講幾句。<br />\n第一，BNO平權唔會割97後，因為我地一向都係爭取救<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">BNO及其後代</span></strong>。，除非你係雙非，否則幾乎一定會受惠。<br />\n第二，BNO平權絕對係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同美國行動有關係</strong></span>，故此毫無疑問就係一個救手足之舉，甚至可能與<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">軍事撤僑</span></strong>有關。<br />\n第三，BNO平到權主要唔係用包機包船黎接香港人去英國，亦都冇咩可能會接，畢竟人數太多。平到權最大重點係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>BNO變正式英國國民，中共逼害英國國民嘅話，英國以至美國就有理由做野</strong></span>。<br />\n第四，BNO平權估計會<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寬鬆處理，英屬香港人（BOTC、BDTC、CUKC）無BNO或者已經過期應該都ok</span></strong>。因為英國情報已經判斷香港情況差到似烏干達難民。<br />\n第五，BNO平權大家可以更加無後顧之憂，因為將來要良民證黎移民，可以向英國當局申請。"},{"pid":"44610427cd43500b6f793069297ca28e17f6b45a","tid":2033812,"uid":358640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c5c612b540ac431aadd83e5b9b414393f103df1","tid":2033812,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:23:42.000Z","msg":"「97前背信棄義<br />\n97後慘被遺棄」？<br />\n<br />\n五毛係咪岸鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實有冇BNO實際上都唔驚<br />\n<br />\n因為「香港人」唔係用政權/地理劃分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人係一樣概念、一個精神、一種價值<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Ideas are bulletproof.<br />\n<br />\nWhen it is circle, be it circle.<br />\nWhen it is square, be it square.<br />\nBe it Water as always.<br />\nBe water my friends.</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:05:15.000Z","msg":"BNO平權有助香港建立海外屬地 黃色經濟圈全球化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2034495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2034495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fc1342a5aa092bff183514ff917a7540b752ea41","tid":2033812,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44610427cd43500b6f793069297ca28e17f6b45a","tid":2033812,"uid":358640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c5c612b540ac431aadd83e5b9b414393f103df1","tid":2033812,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:23:42.000Z","msg":"「97前背信棄義<br />\n97後慘被遺棄」？<br />\n<br />\n五毛係咪岸鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實有冇BNO實際上都唔驚<br />\n<br />\n因為「香港人」唔係用政權/地理劃分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人係一樣概念、一個精神、一種價值<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Ideas are bulletproof.<br />\n<br />\nWhen it is circle, be it circle.<br />\nWhen it is square, be it square.<br />\nBe it Water as always.<br />\nBe water my friends.</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:05:15.000Z","msg":"BNO平權有助香港建立海外屬地 黃色經濟